      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Continuum elastoplastic model with isotropic hardening appropriate for Ti-6Al-4V screw and CoCr rod; contact modeled with augmented Lagrangian formulation.",
      "rationale": "Bilinear isotropic hardening model calibrated to coupon tensile data for Ti-6Al-4V (screw) and CoCr (rod). Frictional contact (mu=0.2) between screw head and rod. Model form appropriate for quasi-static monotonic loading regime of ASTM F1717. Gradation 2 satisfied."
