      "rationale": "Elastic modulus, yield stress, and tangent modulus obtained from tensile coupon testing of production Ti-6Al-4V lot (n=5 coupons). Rod geometry confirmed via coordinate measuring machine. Uncertainty in material inputs propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000 samples); coefficient of variation < 3% for all QoIs. Gradation 2 achieved."
