      "rationale": "Eleven non-cannulated 7.5 mm pedicle screw constructs assembled from production components. Lot traceability confirmed. Constructs distributed across two independent laboratories (n=6, n=5) to assess inter-laboratory variability. Sample size sufficient for Gradation 2 per ASME V&V 40 Table 1."
