      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA boundary conditions replicate experimental fixture constraints within documented tolerance; applied displacement profile matches test machine output.",
      "rationale": "Experimental fixture geometry digitized and replicated in FEA. Applied displacement ramp matched to test machine crosshead displacement log (±0.05 mm). Grip compliance characterized and incorporated as a spring element. Equivalency confirmed via pre-test correlation run. Gradation 2 satisfied."
