      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and absolute percent difference < 10% relative to experimental mean. Validation metric computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 8. Gradation 2 achieved for all QoIs."
